sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as Platform Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.3
    participant KRBAC as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP TLS
    participant VLLM as vLLM API Server<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Runner as HPUModelRunner<br/>In-process
    participant HPU as Intel Gaudi HPU<br/>PCIe/RDMA

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 1: Model Inference Request

    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Gateway->>KRBAC: Forward (TLS/8443)<br/>RBAC validation
    KRBAC->>VLLM: Forward (HTTP/8000)<br/>localhost, no auth
    VLLM->>Runner: Process request<br/>In-process Python
    Runner->>HPU: Execute model forward pass<br/>PCIe/RDMA, HPU graph
    HPU-->>Runner: Inference result (tokens)
    Runner-->>VLLM: Generated tokens
    VLLM-->>KRBAC: JSON Response
    KRBAC-->>Gateway: Response (TLS)
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response (HTTPS)

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 2: Multi-HPU Tensor Parallel Inference

    participant RayHead as Ray Head<br/>6379/TCP, 10001/TCP
    participant Worker0 as HPUWorker Rank 0<br/>HCCL
    participant WorkerN as HPUWorker Rank N<br/>HCCL

    RayHead->>Worker0: Distribute work<br/>Ray internal protocol
    RayHead->>WorkerN: Distribute work<br/>Ray internal protocol
    Worker0->>WorkerN: all-reduce / all-gather<br/>HCCL, Dynamic port, No encryption
    WorkerN-->>Worker0: Collective result
    Worker0-->>RayHead: Inference complete

    Note over Client,HPU: Flow 3: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (NIXL KV Transfer)

    participant PrefillW as Prefill Worker<br/>HPU
    participant HostBuf as Host Memory Buffer
    participant DecodeW as Decode Worker<br/>NIXL UCX/TCP

    PrefillW->>HostBuf: DMA transfer (HPU→CPU)<br/>KV cache data
    HostBuf->>DecodeW: UCX/TCP transfer<br/>Dynamic port, No encryption
    DecodeW->>DecodeW: DMA load (CPU→HPU)<br/>KV cache into decode HPU
